What is it?
===========

This is an active application plugin for the Xfce panel, version 4.8 or higher. It
displays the icon and name of the active application. It also provides a window menu for the active window.

Installation
============

The file 'INSTALL' contains generic installation instructions. For more
detailed information, visit the Sample plugin website at
http://goodies.xfce.org/projects/panel-plugins/xfce4-sample-plugin